blocks.text: The eight men's squads for the inaugural season of The Hundred were revealed on 23 February when the outcome of the previous day's behind-closed-doors player draft was revealed.
Here are how the squads are shaping up so far. The women's squads will be finalised in June.
<italic>If this page is not displaying correctly, </italic><link><caption>please go here</caption><url href="https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/cricket/54646061" platform="highweb"/></link>
Men's teams will be able to add one 'wildcard' player after the T20 Blast.
